(79, 'widget_text', 'a:9:{i:1;a:0:{}i:2;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:5:"About";s:4:"text";s:243:"EthisCrowd.com is the world''s first Real Estate Islamic Crowdfunding Platform. \r\n\r\nOur international community of 17,000 private investors crowdfunds investments in entrepreneurial, business, trade and Real Estate activities in Emerging Asia. ";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:3;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:20:"Important Disclaimer";s:4:"text";s:1513:"This website and the contents herein do not constitute as any financial advice, investment advice or solicitation for the purposes of making financial investments or real estate transactions in Singapore or other territories. Ethis Pte. Ltd. is a firm specialising in the matching of opportunities to members of its private investment club named Ethis Crowd. With regard to these opportunities, the need and onus to do due diligence lies squarely with our members as we do not profess to advise on the same. All dealings and transactions are directly with the businesses, project owners or authorized agents we refer to our members. Ethis Pte. Ltd. is not registered under the Securities & Futures Act of Singapore or the Financial Advisor''s Act under the Monetary Authority of Singapore and thus cannot solicit and manage funds from the public. In relation to real estate transactions, we state that we are not and do not carry out the business of estate agencies nor do we act as estate agents for our members. Where necessary and relevant, we may match our members to estate agents and professionals in the relevant jurisdiction where there may be potentially good returns. This is part of the services provided to Ethis Crowd members in our role as introducers and business-matching specialists. Ethis Crowd members may also be offered Real Estate opportunities in Indonesia by PT Ethis Indo Asia, which is a Singapore-owned Real Estate Development and Investment company registered and licensed in Indonesia.";s:6:"filter";b:1;}i:5;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:1136:"<img src="https://ethisaficf.ethisdev.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/logo_landscape_white.png"/> \r\n\r\nEthisAfrica is a crowdfunding platform where only profitable projects meeting a specific set of Ethical and Social criteria will be listed on the platform and open to the investors crowd. All the necessary info about each project will be provided in order to help investors make a sound investment decision. Once the crowdfunding campaign is successful, the funds raised are directly injected into the project based on a Profit Sharing Agreement signed between Investors and Project Owners. Then, the realised profits of the project will be shared between the contracting parties as agreed initially. Read more <a href="/about-us">About Us</a> and our family of various Ethical & Islamic Crowdfunding/P2P Platforms.\r\n\r\n\r\n<div id="social">\r\n<a class="facebookBtn smGlobalBtn" href="https://www.facebook.com/EthisCrowd/" target="_blank"></a><a class="twitterBtn smGlobalBtn" href="https://twitter.com/EthisCrowd" target="_blank"></a><a class="linkedinBtn smGlobalBtn" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/4857006" target="_blank"></a>	";s:6:"filter";b:1;}i:6;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:1709:"[krown_column width="1/2" el_position="first "]\r\n<strong>Note</strong>\r\n<br />\r\nThis is where you can view your investment participation in Ethiscrowd.\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease remember to update your account details in the account tab.\r\n[/krown_column][krown_column width="1/2" el_position="last "]\r\n<strong>Ethis Credits</strong>\r\n<br />\r\nYour account may be reimbursed with Ethis Credits. Each Ethis credit is equivalent to $1SGD at the prevailing market rate.\r\n<br /><br />\r\nYou may choose to pay the initial admin investment via credits and deduct the remaining investment amount via credits as well.\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease inform the investment manager should you choose to conduct your investments via credits.\r\n[/krown_column]\r\n<strong>Your investments</strong>\r\n<br />\r\nUpon successful transaction of the initial admin investment, <strong>our investment manager will be in touch with you via your email or mobile number.</strong> \r\n<br />\r\nThese details are taken from your account details in the accounts tab.\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou may keep track of the investment progress on the project page itself. Project updates will be released upon reaching significant milestones.\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<strong>Your support is important to us</strong>\r\n<br />\r\nYour support as investors is important to us. You may contact your investment manager during office hours should you face with any problems.\r\n<br /><br />\r\nAlternatively, please use our contact form and we will get back to you within 4 hours (during office hours).\r\n<br /><br />\r\n[krown_button url="https://ethisaficf.ethisdev.com/contact/" size="medium" style="normal" target="_blank" label="Contact Form"][krown_column width="1/2" el_position="first "]";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:7;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:5:"Note:";s:4:"text";s:655:"<strong>Thank you for your interest.</strong>\r\n<br/>\r\nThere is a minimum of S$100 deposit required for all investment applications.\r\n<br/>\r\n<strong>Direct Investment</strong>\r\nYou may choose to make a direct investment payment for the entire investment amount here via credit card, Paypal, BitCoin or Ethis Credits.\r\n<br/>\r\n<strong> Investment Booking</strong>\r\nAlternatively, you may choose to deposit a S$100 to make an investment application booking. This amount is returnable should you decide not to proceed ahead with your investment.\r\n<br/>\r\nOur Investment Manager will contact your upon successful receipt of your application or direct investment.";s:6:"filter";b:1;}i:8;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:5:"Ethis";s:4:"text";s:91:"We empower middle-income investors from around the world to enter Asian markets, ethically.";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:10;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:1910:"<strong>Acknowledgement and Disclaimer</strong>\r\n\r\nYou agree that you use the Website at your own risk. This website and the contents herein do not constitute as any financial advice, investment advice or solicitation for the purposes of making financial investments or real estate transactions in South Africa or other territories. Ethis Africa Pty. Ltd. is a firm specialising in the matching of opportunities to those who register themselves as members on the Ethis Crowd platform. With regard to these opportunities, the need and onus to do due diligence lies squarely with our members as we do not profess to advise on the same. All dealings and transactions are directly with the businesses, project owners or authorized agents we refer to our members.\r\n\r\nEthis Africa Pty Ltd. is not registered under the Financial Advisers and Intermediary Services (FAIS) Act of the Republic of South Africa or the Securities Services Act of the Republic of South Africa and thus cannot solicit and manage funds from the public. In relation to real estate transactions, we state that we are not and do not carry out the business of estate agencies nor do we act as estate agents for our members. Where necessary and relevant, we may match our members to estate agents and professionals in the relevant jurisdiction where there may be potentially good returns. This is part of the services provided to Ethis Crowd members in our role as introducers and business-matching specialists.\r\n\r\n<strong>Governing Law</strong>\r\n\r\nThese terms and Conditions shall be governed by, construed and enforced by the Republic of South African Law. You agree to submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the Republic of South Africa courts.\r\n\r\n<strong>Complaints</strong>\r\n\r\nIf a member has a complaint about the services operated by the Company, it should be communicated to the Company via email at: <a href="#">admin@ethisafrica.com</a>";s:6:"filter";b:1;}s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;}', 'yes'),
