(1154, 7, '2017-03-16 12:42:00', '2017-03-16 04:42:00', '[krown_section background="#ffffff"]\n\n[krown_column width="1/2" el_position="first "]\n<h1>We are a small\nbut active group of\npassionate individuals.</h1>\n[/krown_column]\n\n[krown_column width="1/2" el_position=" last"]\n\nEthisAfrica is the Ethical Social crowdfunding gateway to the African Market. EthisAfrica offers a new platform for project owners to raise funds from a large crowd of investors, and gives the opportunity to small and retail investors to invest their money in highly Ethical, Social and Profitable projects.\n\nPut together by talented and reputable South African partners, EthisAfrica aims to be the African reference and driver towards a world-class investment crowdfunding platform. EthisAfrica aspires to enable better access for project owners to more liquidity and enable small investors to grow their wealth in line with their Ethical and Social values.\n\nEthisAfrica is the African outcome of a strategic partnership with EthisCrowd, a successful Singaporean crowdfunding platform, with an investor-crowd base of  more than 20,000 all over the world, that promotes Islamic and Social peer-to-peer financing in the South East Asian markets.\n\n[/krown_column]\n\n[/krown_section]\n\n[krown_section background="#F8F8F8"]\n\n[krown_column width="1/3" el_position="first "] [/krown_column]\n\n[krown_column width="1/3" el_position=""]\n<blockquote>EthisAfrica envisages to serve the African community with an ethical and socially responsible platform to invest funds in projects with greater social and economic impact. Our mission is to empower small and big investors with the opportunity to grow not only their revenue, but also their contribution to society.\n\n<em>- Mission Statement</em></blockquote>\n[/krown_column]\n\n[krown_column width="1/3" el_position="last"] [/krown_column]\n\n[/krown_section]\n\n[krown_section background="white"]\n\n[krown_column width="1/3" el_position="first "]     [/krown_column] [krown_column width="1/3" el_position=" "]\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Values</h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Interest-Free and Risk Sharing financing: most of the financial crises in the last century were the result of wild capitalism, infinite compounded interest and risk shifting financing. Ensuring a stable financial system and protecting people’s wealth start from an interest-free economy and real sector financing based on risk sharing.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Social and Economic value-adding financing: financialization of economies drives industry players’ focus away from social and economic impacts towards more profit-centered economies. Such behavior resulted in massive social and environmental externalities the world suffers today from. Our focus is rather more oriented towards a balance between profit, people and the environment.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Empowering underprivileged communities: the cornerstone of any healthy economy is the strength of the middle class and the narrow gap between social ranks. By contributing to the empowerment of underprivileged communities, together we build stronger societies and healthier economies.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Full Transparency: the platform require all projects’ owners to provide a comprehensive transparent projects’ disclosure to all investors in order to equip them with all necessary information that will help them make their investment decision.</li>\n</ul>\n[/krown_column] [krown_column width="1/3" el_position=" last"]    [/krown_column]\n\n[/krown_section]\n\n[krown_section background=""]\n\n[krown_column width="1/1" el_position=" "]\n\n[krown_button url="https://ethisaficf.ethisdev.com/faq/" size="small" style="normal" target="_self" label="Read Frequently Asked Question"]\n\n[/krown_column]\n\n[/krown_section]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[krown_section background="white"]\n\n[krown_column width="1/1" el_position=" "]\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Objectives</h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>To provide an alternative financing mode: EthisAfrica believes in the necessity of developing a fair and ethical alternative to the conventional financing mode by promoting risk sharing financing</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n 	<li>To provide quick liquidity: EthisAfrica is using crowdfunding technology as a tool to provide quick liquidity to finance value-adding projects</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n 	<li>To empower small investors: EthisAfrica enables investment access to all types of investors -low/middle class and youth - to generate revenue from their small investments.</li>\n</ul>\n[/krown_column]\n\n[/krown_section]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '927-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-03-16 12:42:00', '2017-03-16 04:42:00', '', 927, 'http://app.ethisaficf.ethisdev.com/2016/06/03/927-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
