D$1,500. Crowdfunding mitigates your investment risks further by spreading it across more people. Everyone wins something with crowdfunding.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n[/krown_column] [krown_column width="1/3" el_position=" last"]    [/krown_column]\r\n[/krown_section]\r\n\r\n[krown_column width="1/2" el_position="first "]<img class="size-medium wp-image-1237 alignright" src="https://ethisaficf.ethisdev.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/computer_image-300x241.png" alt="computer_image" width="300" height="241" /> [/krown_column]\r\n[krown_column width="1/2" el_position="last "]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">We have processed\r\nSGD$ 3.6 million into projects\r\nto build 5,000 affordable homes.\r\nRealised returns average 10% to 16%.</h2>\r\n[/krown_column]\r\n<h5 style="text-align: center;">Trusted and Seen in</h5>\r\n<div class="tg-wrap">\r\n<table class="tg">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class="tg-yw4l"><img class="alignnone wp-image-1224 size-full" src="https://ethisaficf.ethisdev.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/business_icon_05.png" width="175" height="50" /></th>\r\n<th class="tg-yw4l"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1222" src="https://ethisaficf.ethisdev.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/business_icon_07.png" alt="business_icon_07" width="175" height="50" /></th>\r\n<th class="tg-yw4l"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1223" src="https://ethisaficf.ethisdev.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/business_icon_06.png" alt="business_icon_06" width="175" height="50" /></th>\r\n<th class="tg-yw4l"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1221" src="https://ethisaficf.ethisdev.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/business_icon_01.png" alt="business_icon_01" width="175" height="50" /></th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="tg-yw4l"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1240" src="https://ethisaficf.ethisdev.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/business_icon_09.png" alt="business_icon_09" width="175" height="50" /></td>\r\n<td class="tg-yw4l"><img class="alignnone 