 the security of personal information. There will be in place an appropriate security procedures and technical and organization measure to safeguard your personal information.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Personal Information</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">You may be required to provide us information about yourself by using the online forms provided on the Website. This includes, without limitation, information you provide when you register to use the Website, enter into a transaction via the Website, participate in discussion boards or other social media functions on the Website and/or when you report a problem with the Website or our services.</p>\r\nThe information you give us may include:\r\n\r\n(a) your name;\r\n(b) your date of birth;\r\n(c) your current and (where necessary) previous postal address;\r\n(d) your telephone number and email address;\r\n(e) Information relating to your employment, income, financial and personal circumstances;\r\n(f) Information relating to ay businesses or companies which you may have an interest; and\r\n(g) Where applicable, specific documents which verify your identity and any other personal information.\r\n<h4>Use of Your Information</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We may use your Information obtained by us as set out in this Privacy</p>\r\nPolicy for the purpose of :\r\n\r\n(a) Delivering our products and Services to you\r\n(b) Improving our products and Services to you\r\n(c) Marketing and Advertising our products and Services to you\r\n(d) to verify your identity in order to prevent and detect money laundering and fraud\r\n(f) to carry out credit reference checks\r\n(g) to carry out market research\r\n(h) to notify you about any changes to our services\r\n(i) to keep you informed about fees and charges\r\n<h4>Updating and correcting your information</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">You have the right to request access to your personal data and to correct your personal if it is or has become inaccurate, incomplete, misleading, misrepresenting, and incorrect. You may request in writing to access to your personal data to change and update your information. However, we have the right to use our discretion in allowing any corrections requested and/or require further documentary evidence of the new data to avoid any fraud or inaccuracy of data.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Third Party Link</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">There may be Third Party Websites provided on the Website. This is for your conveniences in accessing to other information and we hold no responsibility for any damage or losses occur by relying on the Third Party Websites. Further this privacy policy only applies to our Website and shall not extend to any third party links. Please ensure that you read their own privacy policies.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Disclosure</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer to third parties your personal information. However, we may also release your information when we believe it is appropriate to comply with the law, enforce our site policies, or protect ours and others’ rights, property or safety. Unless permitted or required to do by law, we will never disclose any information which is classified as “sensitive personal data” without your explicit consent.</p>', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'privacy-policy', '', '', '2017-01-17 18:12:58', '2017-01-17 10:12:58', '', 0, 'http://ethiscrowd:8888/?page_id=1438', 0, 'page', '', 0),
