 Statement</em></blockquote>\r\n[/krown_column]\r\n\r\n[krown_column width="1/4" el_position="last"] [/krown_column]\r\n\r\n[krown_column width="1/3" el_position="first "]     [/krown_column] [krown_column width="1/3" el_position=" "]\r\nValues\r\n\r\nInterest-Free and Risk Sharing financing: most of the financial crises in the last century were the result of wild capitalism, infinite compounded interest and risk shifting financing. Ensuring a stable financial system and protecting people’s wealth start from an interest-free economy and real sector financing based on risk sharing.\r\n\r\n\r\nSocial and Economic value-adding financing: financialization of economies drives industry players’ focus away from social and economic impacts towards more profit-centered economies. Such behavior resulted in massive social and environmental externalities the world suffers today from. Our focus is rather more oriented towards a balance between profit, people and the environment.\r\n\r\n\r\nEmpowering underprivileged communities: the cornerstone of any healthy economy is the strength of the middle class and the narrow gap between social ranks. By contributing to the empowerment of underprivileged communities, together we build stronger societies and healthier economies.\r\n\r\n\r\nFull Transparency: the platform require all projects’ owners to provide a comprehensive transparent projects’ disclosure to all investors in order to equip them with all necessary information that will help them make their investment decision.\r\n[/krown_column] [krown_column width="1/3" el_position=" last"]    [/krown_column]\r\n\r\n[krown_column width="1/2" el_position="first "]\r\n\r\n[/krown_column]\r\n\r\n[krown_column width="1/2" el_position=" last"]\r\n\r\n[/krown_column]\r\n\r\n[/krown_section]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2572-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-16 11:41:08', '2017-03-16 03:41:08', '', 2572, 'https://ethisaficf.ethisdev.com/2572-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision',